OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTaliban to force Afghan    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwomen to wear face veil    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Afghan women will have to wear the     
OL,6, Islamic face veil for the first time in
OL,7, decades under a decree passed by the   
OL,8, country's ruling Taliban militants.    
OL,10,FAny woman who refuses to comply and    
OL,11,Fignores official warnings to male      
OL,12,Fmembers of her family could see a male 
OL,13,Fguardian jailed for three days.        
OL,15,FThe Taliban enforced the               
OL,16,Fall-encompassing burka during their    
OL,17,Ffirst stint in power in the 1990s.     
OL,19,FBut they had not enforced it in Afghan 
OL,20,Fcities since taking over last year.    
